<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>NFS-e Bikon Tecnologia</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f3f7f8;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#15202b;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#f3f7f8;margin:0;padding:28px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:0 14px;">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width:640px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #dbe8ea;box-shadow:0 8px 26px rgba(11,31,42,0.08);">
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#061018;padding:26px 30px;border-bottom:4px solid #00b8be;">
              <div style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:2.5px;color:#00dee1;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;">Bikon Tecnologia</div>
              <div style="font-size:26px;line-height:32px;color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;margin-top:8px;">NFS-e emitida</div>
              <div style="font-size:14px;line-height:21px;color:#b8c9ce;margin-top:8px;">Documento fiscal referente aos serviços prestados.</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:30px;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;color:#15202b;">Olá,</p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 22px;font-size:16px;line-height:24px;color:#15202b;">Segue em anexo a NFS-e emitida pela <strong>Bikon Tecnologia</strong> referente à competência <strong>{competencia}</strong>.</p>

              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0;margin:0 0 24px;background:#f8fbfc;border:1px solid #dbe8ea;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid #dbe8ea;font-size:13px;color:#53656c;width:38%;">Cliente</td>
                  <td style="padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid #dbe8ea;font-size:14px;color:#15202b;font-weight:700;">{cliente_nome}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid #dbe8ea;font-size:13px;color:#53656c;">Competência</td>
                  <td style="padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid #dbe8ea;font-size:14px;color:#15202b;font-weight:700;">{competencia}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid #dbe8ea;font-size:13px;color:#53656c;">Valor</td>
                  <td style="padding:16px 18px;border-bottom:1px solid #dbe8ea;font-size:14px;color:#15202b;font-weight:700;">R$ {valor_total}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:16px 18px;font-size:13px;color:#53656c;">Número da NFS-e</td>
                  <td style="padding:16px 18px;font-size:14px;color:#15202b;font-weight:700;">{numero_nfse}</td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <div style="background:#e9fbfc;border-left:4px solid #00b8be;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 18px;margin:0 0 24px;">
                <div style="font-size:14px;line-height:21px;color:#16343a;">Anexos enviados neste e-mail: <strong>PDF da NFS-e</strong> e <strong>XML fiscal</strong>.</div>
              </div>

              <p style="margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;line-height:23px;color:#15202b;">Qualquer dúvida, é só responder este e-mail.</p>
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;line-height:23px;color:#15202b;">Atenciosamente,<br><strong>Faturamento Bikon</strong></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#f7fbfc;padding:18px 30px;border-top:1px solid #dbe8ea;">
              <div style="font-size:12px;line-height:18px;color:#6a7f86;">Bikon Tecnologia · Infraestrutura de rede, SNOC, backup em nuvem e gerenciamento de redes corporativas.</div>
              <div style="font-size:12px;line-height:18px;color:#6a7f86;margin-top:6px;">Este é um envio automático do faturamento. Responda este e-mail se precisar falar com a equipe.</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
